RMendeley 1.2
================

* Lincense moved from BSD to CC0 (public domain declaration)

RMendeley 1.1
================

* bugfix -- removed outdated demo file

RMendeley 1.0.0
================

* Added Oauth authentication using ROAuth 0.9.2 which now allows users to manage their entire Mendeley collection directly from R.
* Added 22 new functions which now allow users to access user specific methods listed in the API documentation: http://apidocs.mendeley.com/home/user-specific-methods
